// Example: External Repository Dependencies (demonstration)
//
// Note: Full repository rules implementation is in progress.
// The syntax below shows the intended API for external dependencies.
//
// When fully implemented, this will enable:
// - HTTP archive with integrity verification
// - Git repository with commit pinning
// - Local filesystem dependencies
//
// Example syntax (not yet fully functional):
//
// repository("fmt") {
//     url: "https://github.com/fmtlib/fmt/releases/download/10.2.1/fmt-10.2.1.zip";
//     integrity: "312151a2d13c8327f5c9c586ac6cf7cddc1658e8f53edae0ec56509c8fa516c9";
//     stripPrefix: "fmt-10.2.1";
// }
//
// See README.md for full documentation and roadmap.

